public class ValidationIssues extends com.telenav.kivakit.core.messaging.listeners.MessageList
A MessageList and MessageCounter that captures validation issues. Any message with a Message.Status worse than or equal to that of a Glitch causes isValid() to return false. In particular, capturing a Glitch or Problem makes this ValidationIssues object invalid.

Validity

  • isValid()

Counting Messages

  • MessageList.count(Message.Status)
  • MessageList.count(Class)
  • MessageList.countWorseThanOrEqualTo(Message.Status)
  • MessageCounter.countWorseThanOrEqualTo(Class)

  • MessageList.matching(Matcher)
  • MessageList.messagesOfType(Class)
